    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html style=\"font-size: 85px;\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"renderer\" content=\"webkit\">\n    <title>清华大学建筑学院</title>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"清华大学建筑学院,建筑学院,世界一流,建筑学,中国特色，城市规划，建筑系\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"清华大学是中国著名高等学府，是中国高层次人才培养和科学技术研究的重要基地。清华大学的前身是清华学堂，成立于1911年。截至2017年，清华大学设有20个学院、58个系，已成为一所具有理学、工学、文学、艺术学、历史学、哲学、经济学、管理学、法学、教育学和医学等学科门类的综合性、研究型、开放式大学。截至2017年8月31号，清华大学在学学生总数为47762人，其中本科生15619人、硕士生19062人、博士生13081人。\">\n   \n    <link href=\"/sites/css/font.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/index.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/phone.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.min.css\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/js.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.jquery.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"headD\"></div>\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"head\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <a href=\"\" class=\"logo\"></a>\n        <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navA\"></a>\n        <dl class=\"btn\">\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" class=\"on\">CN</a></dd>\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/Home\">EN</a></dd>\n            \n            \n \n            \n            \n            <dd class=\"search\" value=\"搜索\"> \n              <form name=\"form1\" id=\"search-form-header\" action=\"/column/search\" target=\"_blank\" method=\"post\">\n                   <div class=\"input\">    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"curpage\" value=\"1\">\n\t               <input name=\"key\" type=\"text\" class=\"inp\" value=\"\" onfocus=\"this.value=''\" onblur=\"if(this.value==''){this.value='';}\">\n                </div>  \n\t         </form>\n        \n           </dd>  \n            <div class=\"submit\">      \n                 <a id=\"searchbtn\" href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"$('#search-form-header').submit();\" class=\"btn\" title=\"搜索\">搜索</a>\n           </div> \n      \n            \n        </dl>\n        <div class=\"nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jj\">简介</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/dt\">动态</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/xs\">系所</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/zs\">招生</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jx\">教学</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/ky\">科研</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/rw\">人物</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jl\">交流</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/lj\">链接</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"characterShow_01\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n         <div class=\"info\"><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a><a href=\"/column/rw\"><b>·</b>人物</a>  <a href=\"/column/sz\"><b>·</b>师资</a>  <a href=\"/column/rw_csgh\"><b>·</b>城市规划系</a>  </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"name\">周政旭</div>\n        <div class=\"msg\">\n            电话：86-10-6278-3328 <br>\n            传真： <br>\n            E-mail：zhouzhengxu@tsinghua.edu.cn\n        </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"/upload_files/image/1593418432355_28.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></div>\n   \n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wal characterShow\">\n   \n     <div class=\"content\"><p><strong>研究方向</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\">乡村规划与设计，聚落研究，历史村镇保护与更新</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong>教育经历</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>2006-2013&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清华大学</span><span>&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">城乡规划博士研究生，获城乡规划专业工学博士学位</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>2002-2006&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清华大学</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">建筑学本科生</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，获建筑学学士学位</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong>工作经历</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>2015-2016&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">意大利罗马第一大学</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px\">SAPIENZA UNIVERSITY OF ROME</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">博士后</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>2013-2015&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清华大学</span><span>&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">博士后</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px 112px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong>学术兼职</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国城市规划学会山地城乡规划学术委员会，副秘书长</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国建筑学会村镇建设分会，委员</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国自然资源学会国土空间规划研究学术委员会，委员</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国明史学会屯堡研究分会，理事</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">《中国大百科全书》</span><span>(</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">第三版</span><span>)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">人居环境科学学科城乡规划分卷编委会，秘书</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>International Conference on Architecture, ICONA, Scientific Committee Member</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 3px 112px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong>课题研究</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">基于县域尺度的贵州贫困地区空间格局、产生机制及规划应对研究，国家自然科学基金青年基金资助项目（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">村镇聚落物质空间数据提取与监测评价，“十三五”国家重点研发计划“村镇聚落空间重构数字化模拟及评价模型”项目子课题（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中国贵州中部与意大利北部山地聚落空间形态比较研究，中国博士后科学基金特别资助项目（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">基于面板数据的贵州县域贫困的空间因子及作用机制研究，中国博士后科学基金面上一等资助项目（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Evolutions and Challenges of Traditional Mountainous Settlements: A Comparative Study of Guizhou Plateau and Italian Mountainous Region<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">，</span>Sapienza University of Rome, International Cooperation Fund<span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">小城镇人居环境综合整治情况调查，住房和城乡建设部研究课题（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">山地民族村镇空间特色提炼与发展路径选择：以黔东南地区为例，清华大学中国新型城镇化研究院开放基金（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">京郊空心村空闲宅基地利用模式调查研究，清华大学—旭辉控股可持续住区联合研究中心课题（负责人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中国人居史研究（主要参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">我国城乡发展力差距研究，住房和城乡建设部研究课题</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">（主要参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">贵州省“美丽乡村、四在农家”人居环境整治研究，贵州省住房和城乡建设厅科技合作项目（主要参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">中国特色城镇化道路战略研究：城市文化与人居建设专题，中国工程院重大咨询研究项目（参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">城乡统筹与人居环境科学发展，中国工程院咨询研究项目（参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 9px; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">基于动态模拟的背景旧城非历史街区空间演变机制与整治设计策略研究，国家自然科学基金面上项目（参加人）</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体\"><br></span></strong></p><p><strong>学术专著</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 28px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">周政旭</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">形成与演变：从文本与空间中探索聚落营建史<span>[M]. </span>北京<span>: </span>中国建筑工业出版社<span>,2016.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 28px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">周政旭</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">, </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">封基铖<span>, </span>等<span>. </span>贵州扁担山<span>-</span>白水河地区布依族族聚落调查研究<span>[M]. </span>北京<span>: </span>中国建筑工业出版社<span>,2018.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 28px;text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">周政旭</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贵州贫困地区县域人居环境建设研究<span>[M]. </span>北京<span>: </span>中国建筑工业出版社<spa